    "title": "Promise",
    "description": "Это ещё цвето́чки, а я́годки впереди́.\n[These are just flowers; berries will come soon.]\n{&quot;Eto escho tsvetochki, a yagodki vperedi&quot;}\n– Russian Proverb.\n\n&quot;The most radical revolutionary will become a conservative the day after the revolution.&quot;\n– Hannah Arendt, in 'The New Yorker' (12 September 1970)\n\n&quot;The sun comes up just about as often as it goes down, in the long run, but this doesn't make its motion random.&quot;\n– Donald Knuth, 'The Art of Computer Programming', Vol. II, 1969, section 3.3.2.",
